---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions - GSTAT Index Generation Tool" description=" terms and conditions of use">
	<Header currentPath="/terms" />
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">

		<!-- Content -->
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
			<article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Terms and Conditions</h1>
				<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">By accessing and using this tool, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this service.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">The tool is a free, client-side web application that helps legal professionals create court bundles by:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Merging multiple PDF documents</li>
					<li>Generating tables of contents</li>
					<li>Adding page numbering and formatting</li>
					<li>Creating hyperlinked indexes and bookmarks</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-gray-700">All processing occurs in your web browser. No files are uploaded to our servers.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Use License</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">BunTool is provided under an open-source license. You are granted permission to:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Use BunTool for personal or commercial purposes</li>
					<li>Generate unlimited court bundles</li>
					<li>Access the source code and modify it for your own use</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-gray-700">You may NOT:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Claim BunTool as your own creation</li>
					<li>Remove copyright notices or attribution</li>
					<li>Use BunTool for illegal purposes</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. No Warranties</h2>
				<div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-600 p-6 my-6">
					<p class="text-yellow-900 font-semibold mb-2">Important Legal Notice</p>
					<p class="text-yellow-800 mb-0">BunTool is provided "AS IS" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not guarantee that BunTool will be error-free, uninterrupted, or suitable for court proceedings.</p>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-700">You acknowledge that:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>BunTool is a tool to assist in bundle creation, not legal advice</li>
					<li>You are responsible for ensuring bundles meet court requirements</li>
					<li>You should verify all generated documents before filing</li>
					<li>Different jurisdictions may have different bundle requirements</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">To the maximum extent permitted by law, BunTool and its creators shall not be liable for:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Any damages arising from use or inability to use BunTool</li>
					<li>Errors, omissions, or inaccuracies in generated documents</li>
					<li>Court rejection of bundles created with BunTool</li>
					<li>Loss of data or documents</li>
					<li>Professional consequences resulting from use of BunTool</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. User Responsibilities</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">As a user of BunTool, you are responsible for:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Ensuring you have rights to all documents you process</li>
					<li>Complying with applicable court rules and practice directions</li>
					<li>Verifying the accuracy of generated bundles</li>
					<li>Maintaining appropriate backups of your documents</li>
					<li>Using a modern, secure web browser</li>
					<li>Protecting confidential information according to professional obligations</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Professional Use</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">If you are a legal professional:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>BunTool does not constitute legal advice or professional services</li>
					<li>You remain solely responsible for work product submitted to courts</li>
					<li>You must comply with your jurisdiction's professional conduct rules</li>
					<li>Client confidentiality obligations remain your responsibility</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Browser Compatibility</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">BunTool requires a modern web browser with JavaScript enabled. We recommend:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge (latest versions)</li>
					<li>Sufficient device memory for processing large PDFs</li>
					<li>Stable internet connection for initial page load (processing is offline)</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Service Availability</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">While we strive to keep BunTool available, we do not guarantee:</p>
				<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Uninterrupted access to the website</li>
					<li>That BunTool will be free from bugs or errors</li>
					<li>Compatibility with future browser versions</li>
					<li>Continued maintenance or development</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Modifications to Terms</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of BunTool after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms. Material changes will be posted on this page.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Governing Law</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">These terms shall be governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">12. Open Source</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">BunTool is open source software. The source code is available for review, modification, and distribution according to the project's open source license.</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">13. Contact</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700">For questions about these terms, please contact us through our GitHub repository or project website.</p>

				<div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 mt-8">
					<p class="text-blue-900 font-semibold mb-2">Summary in Plain English</p>
					<p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">BunTool is a free tool that we provide to help you create court bundles. It works in your browser, so your files stay private. We've made it as good as we can, but you're responsible for checking the final bundle meets your needs and court requirements. Use it wisely!</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
